            "title": "Assessing the accuracy of interviewed recall for rare, highly seasonal events: the case of wildlife consumption in Madagascar",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "C. D.",
                    "lastName": "Golden"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
